<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/533868-who-murdered-the-baron-why">who murdered the Baron? Why?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_533868'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F447895.The_Leper_of_Saint_Giles">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/533868-who-murdered-the-baron-why">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/533868-who-murdered-the-baron-why">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/8163331-meg"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1331561562i/8163331._UY100_CR17,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/8163331-meg">Meg</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Simon murdered the Baron, his uncle, because he would then inherit his property and be able to marry Iveta de Massard. Simon took the opportunity beca<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Simon murdered the Baron, his uncle, because he would then inherit his property and be able to marry Iveta de Massard. Simon took the opportunity because Joscelin behaved rashly and made himself the likely culprit. It is suggested that Simon thought he would get away with Joscelin being found guilty and had been planning the murder for awhile, just waiting for a suitable chance. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
</div>
