<div id="review_3352492710" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3352492710" />
    <a title="Tara " class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/46920502-tara"><img alt="Tara " src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1506707450p2/46920502.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3352492710?book_show_action=true">Jan 12, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Tara " class="user" itemprop="url" name="Tara " href="/user/show/46920502-tara">Tara </a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/46920502-tara?shelf=owned">owned</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/46920502-tara?shelf=brother-cadfael-chronicles">brother-cadfael-chronicles</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3352492710" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1156068124608747578">I am always amazed at what a stellar job Peters does at transporting her readers back to medieval times. Her characters, her plotting, and her dialogue all ring true, and make for compelling reading. There are some repetitive themes from book to book, leading to a bit of predictability in where the story is going, but that does not detract from a fun read. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

