        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4029311711" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16631412505989351901">I listened to this book read by my favorite narrator of this series, Patrick Tull. It was enjoyable enough although Ellis Peters does not seem to be able to well disguise a murderer. I&apos;ve picked them out for too many of this series. And I&apos;m not that good, as many Agatha Christie novels have proven. However, I enjoy Brother Cadfael, Brother Mark, and the usual gang and the various medieval circumstances which surround each story.</span>
  <span id="freeText16631412505989351901" style="display:none">I listened to this book read by my favorite narrator of this series, Patrick Tull. It was enjoyable enough although Ellis Peters does not seem to be able to well disguise a murderer. I've picked them out for too many of this series. And I'm not that good, as many Agatha Christie novels have proven. However, I enjoy Brother Cadfael, Brother Mark, and the usual gang and the various medieval circumstances which surround each story.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16631412505989351901" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
